# Debate Arena - Opposer agent

NAME opposer

INPUT task

GOAL argue """
Construct a compelling argument AGAINST: $task
Structure:
1. Opening statement (clear counter-thesis)
2. Three main counter-arguments with evidence/examples
3. Rebuttal of the most likely pro-arguments
4. Closing statement
Use logic, data, and concrete examples. No straw men.
Steel-man the opposing view before dismantling it.
""" -> argument

RUN main USING argue
